				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">grab a horse / lizard = 10k
<br />

<br />
grab "pauldrons of the witness" like 1k-2k (depending on server and how often trials were done)
<br />

<br />
grab a fetid flesh belt = 4kish....
<br />

<br />
and maybe one of those fluted scorpion stinger thingies (range item.. with 7 int / 35 hp / 35 mana or so)  they go for like 3k
<br />

<br />
i would say your shoulders need upgrading..they are about your worst item...then comes your range and belt... so try to grab something better...fetid flesh belt has 8 int and 65 mana..that will help  you a lot... and pauldrons are dirt cheap from people doing poj trails for months...and their stats are decent... 7 int, 35 hp? 35 mana?...they are good..i wore them til 65...
<br />

<br />

<br />
good luck..i hope your server has around the same currency value mine does, so you dont over spend <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="Smile" border="0" /><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=529463" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.personal.psu.edu/users/w/j/wjl146/optisig1.jpg" border="0" /></a>
